### 最长连续登录天数

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)



解：

1.先给每个UID的loadtime排序 (a)表

```sql
select UID,loadtime,row_number() over(partition by UID order by loadtime) as t_rank

from table
```

2.求出每一段的分组情况以及开始和结束的时间和间隔差 (b)表

使用函数date_sub()做日期倒退，

group by以后计算的都是每一分组内的

```sql
select UID,date_sub(loadtime,t_rank) as date_group,min(loadtime) as start_time,max(loadtime) as end_time, count(1) as continue_days

from a

group by UID,date_sub(loadtime,t_rank) 
```

3.从中选出UID和对应最长的时间

```sql
select UID,max(continue_days) as continue

from b

group by UID
```
